cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.CR 

This paper focuses on trajectory-based prediction using machine learning techniques, specifically Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs) and Attention-based RNNs. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with spatial and temporal data, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The use of attention mechanisms and Bluetooth data also suggests that it could belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
